WEBVTT

00:00:02.753 --> 00:00:06.008
Saida Aden Said: Ko'z oldimdan
haligacha mudhish tasvirlar ketmaydi:

00:00:06.032 --> 00:00:08.322
odamlarning yiqilishi,

00:00:08.346 --> 00:00:09.510
o'q ovozlari.

00:00:09.534 --> 00:00:10.862
Rosa qo'rqardim.

00:00:10.886 --> 00:00:13.095
Chindan ham, juda ko'p yig'lardim.

00:00:13.119 --> 00:00:16.455
Ota-onami tanigan kimdir, 
qo'limdan tutib,

00:00:16.479 --> 00:00:18.443
"Ketdik! Ketdik!" dedi.

00:00:18.467 --> 00:00:21.324
Men esa, "Onam qayerda? 
Oyijonim qani?" deb qoldim.

00:00:22.245 --> 00:00:25.341
Noria Dambrine Dusabireme: 
Tunlari o'q ovozlarini eshitardik,

00:00:25.365 --> 00:00:26.558
qurol ovozlarini.

00:00:26.582 --> 00:00:28.276
Saylovlar bo'lishi kerak edi.

00:00:28.300 --> 00:00:30.847
Yoshlarimiz ko'chalarda,